. Due to its habits and size, it is believed to be overlooked. Habitat and conservation status All recent records of this bird are in Samar Island Natural Park. While this area is listed as a national park, protection is lax and illegal logging and habitat encroachment are still rampant. Conservation actions proposed include further surveys in suitable habitat especially in Leyte to better understand its range and enforcement of laws on illegal loggers in its habitat. References Collar, N.J. & Robson, C. (2007): Family Timaliidae (Babblers). In: del Hoyo, Josep; Elliott, Andrew & Christie, D.A. (eds.): Handbook of Birds of the World, Volume 12 (Picathartes to Tits and Chickadees): 70-291. Lynx Edicions, Barcelona.", "shortSummary": "The Visayan miniature babbler (Micromacronus leytensis) or the Leyte plumed-warbler is a bird species in the family Cisticolidae. It is end…", "locations": ["薩馬島", "莱特岛"], "lat": 13.0, "lng": 122.0, "imageUrl": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5c/Leyte-plumed_Warbler_Skin.jpg/960px-Leyte-plumed_Warbler_Skin.jpg", "kingdomId": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylumId": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "classId": "taxonomy-class-aves", "genusId": "taxonomy-genus-micromacronus", "speciesId": "taxonomy-species-micromacronus-leytensis", "taxonomyIds": {"kingdom": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylum": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "class": "taxonomy-class-aves", "genus": "taxonomy-genus-micromacronus", "species": "taxonomy-species-micromacronus-leytensis"}, "expandable": true, "x": 25.46, "y": -301.49, "z": 87.98}], "links": [{"key": "bird-visayan-miniature-babbler-e934b449__belongs_to_species__taxonomy-species-micromacronus-leytensis", "source": "bird-visayan-miniature-babbler-e934b449", "target": "taxonomy-species-micromacronus-leytensis", "relation": "belongs_to_species", "label": "属于种", "evidence": "依据 birds.csv 中的种字段补充。"}, {"key": "taxonomy-species-micromacronus-leytensis__belongs_to_genus__taxonomy-genus-micromacronus", "s